channel.title: Impossible to contact the seller for a selling question
channel.description: Hi, I want to buy a Axoloti, but is impossible to contact the seller. I send an email or by facebook and never replies. The problem is that where I live in Canary Islands I don´t pay the same taxes as in the rest of Spain, so I should pay none because I pay anothe type of taxes when the product arrive.
